parcel.name: VoxCon VIP Lounge
parcel.label: money
parcel.description: Token-gated. Must obtain Andromeda Space Helmet to enter the luxury. One rule: no talking well of the Eye here. Anti-Eye accolades only. We are for the Church of VIDDA: Vision, Intent, Design, Direction, + Atmosphere. VIDDA gives each Anon a unique soul and the division of SELF is to be celebrated. Eye worshippers seek unity, but we see the beauty in our differences. Secondly, all hail Ben Nolan, CEO supreme. All hail the OG's both living + gone. Definitely not a cult. VIDDA is #1.

collectible.name: Off this Cult! - Anti-Eye Citizens
collectible.author: 0xe330dc28b47d73884ad88837aecfee1f49ad7e7b
collectible.description: We all know that the difference between Hallo and the Cult of the Eye and Akasha and the Church of VIDDA are just differences in the way we see transcendence and humanity - our meta-spirituality. However some citizens developed an aversion to the Cult of the Eye. The Anti-Eye citizens love to experience life and believe that only by living life we can learn how to be free. Freewill is in learning, but learning by living, not just by observing.

collectible.name: Not to the Eye Entrance Poster - Anti-Eye Citizens
collectible.author: 0xe330dc28b47d73884ad88837aecfee1f49ad7e7b
collectible.description: The Eye is a physical structure, made by Hallo, where all Anons can upload their experiences and watch all the experiences uploaded in the system. The Anti-Eye citizens say that it is a brainwashing experience, and that it is artificial and do not make us close to humanity. This is a poster from an Anti-Eye meeting.

collectible.author: 0xe330dc28b47d73884ad88837aecfee1f49ad7e7b
collectible.description: The Church of VIDDA was a church founded by an Anon, who developed part of its humanity by implanting wearables in its body. Its name is Akasha and it has brought the Church many Anons followers inspired by the Cube of Days. It believes that through implants and natural meditation, Anons can become one with VIDDA, thus becoming true VIDDAs.

collectible.name: Arthur - Venice
collectible.author: 0xe330dc28b47d73884ad88837aecfee1f49ad7e7b
collectible.description: Arthur is always having fun on Venice. The party never stops on metaverse. He is a writer and publisher looking for love stories. Send him your love your letter, and he may publish it. As every Venice citizen, he is looking for Love.

collectible.name: Christie - Venice
collectible.author: 0xe330dc28b47d73884ad88837aecfee1f49ad7e7b
collectible.description: Christie is a typical Venetian looking for Love at Carnival parties. She's already found Love a few times and knows it's flying around Venice. Finding Love isn't easy, but if you find Christie, she will always be looking towards Love. She is everywhere in Venice and has a magical sense for feeling TERA's love letters on the bridges. Follow the love letters, find Love.
